rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d2017f2b4405f9a30154718354c3b6aa297150","tid":442030,"uid":93141,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T23:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係條片入面果個人講得好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n始終外國人嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都好普遍,學校有幾個local tutor就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659347eb8939c85350ae67316f5f749bae2d8c26","tid":442030,"uid":93141,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T23:46:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔關好唔好聽事<br />\n我覺得香港口音既英文真係代表到香港<br />\n好特別 其他國家學唔到<br />\n係外國聽到有人講緊香港口音既英文會覺得好親切 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係,所以我成篇都冇話香港口音好聽,親切感先係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就好似要你揀同陌生既靚女定易相處性格好既中上女拍拖,緊係揀後者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdbc88d787884d443c58006064e8b838c5d662a","tid":442030,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:10:21.000Z","msg":"一個英國都有幾百種口音，成撚日互相笑大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當中以紐卡素口音最撚難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd14ad57abac79572da95e0cbfbfceb75eeafe2e","tid":442030,"uid":93141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:15:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個英國都有幾百種口音，成撚日互相笑大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當中以紐卡素口音最撚難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果scot都計既話我覺得Scottish accent最難頂,完全聽唔明,溝通都有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd262991bee03ee86edc7367c7711c938db735a8","tid":442030,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:23:53.000Z","msg":"同港女扮abc比簡直係侮辱廣東口音"},{"pid":"fe359f30f9cfc65c121392e01d2b93e5f6f3fdca","tid":442030,"uid":136588,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:25:36.000Z","msg":"其實外國人唔介意你咩口音...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c0a0d07a8d2654863dacf537ee518218db8f72","tid":442030,"uid":3602,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:27:21.000Z","msg":"出嚟做嘢未"},{"pid":"371ffd462accedbb72a41192fee86a584f36b6a1","tid":442030,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:34:41.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得口音係cultural identity既一種，香港人講英文緊係有香港口音架啦<br />\n讀得啱同識分輕重音咪得"},{"pid":"545f8adfa2257c49f3e07be5dc43f1bdddc0fe10","tid":442030,"uid":116360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:39:28.000Z","msg":"其實香港口音包唔包括唔係好識讀consonant clusters 比如present-&gt;pesent, prove-&gt;pove/plove"},{"pid":"2116995c4060dc2d4526af35e8a21823f16bbacc","tid":442030,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:40:48.000Z","msg":"連音都發唔正 咩香港口音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56186abbeb796ceb6833ef7983a381f6401e142e","tid":442030,"uid":93141,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:46:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出嚟做嘢未</blockquote><br />\n冇正統藍血連登仔咁勁個個都google,goldman sachs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係去過兩次歐洲做intern,黎緊可能去荷蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留左幾個月都冇因為口音而被惡意攻擊,因為大家都來自世界各地,溝通時識互相尊重,當然可能係文明地方先有咁既概念啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d51741503c75d657f81119403d2df966f09d38","tid":442030,"uid":127292,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:50:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df43b6c5d7dfa274d4fac74e7e69c8d17208ab43","tid":442030,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:54:35.000Z","msg":"應該係，嚴謹而言，英文當中真係有香港口音，定只係香港人學英文學錯發音，亂混用美＆英式文法＆口音？"},{"pid":"3367569557aea68bad2b5e169c95b30637d92c9a","tid":442030,"uid":93141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:54:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實香港口音包唔包括唔係好識讀consonant clusters 比如present-&gt;pesent, prove-&gt;pove/plove</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>連音都發唔正 咩香港口音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n包唔包係個好問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先咩叫&quot;讀得正&quot;先?<br />\n如果所有人發音都係跟牛津英文標準既話,最後個個字正腔圓就只會得返好撚posh既英國口音<br />\n所以我覺得口音會包埋讀唔讀得&ldquo;正呢件事,如果真係要執,同係UK既scottish同irish accent用牛津標準睇都係錯撚曬既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者熟悉既例子係廣州白話vs香港廣東話,中國普通話vs台灣國語,大家都係覺得對方講得唔&quot;正&quot;,但係分別真係得語言既文化背景同口音咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ab7f4414b7257d850388042ecd4dc62bf08894","tid":442030,"uid":93141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T00:59:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係，嚴謹而言，英文當中真係有香港口音，定只係香港人學英文學錯發音，亂混用美＆英式文法＆口音？</blockquote><br />\n樓下再補充少少,你可能覺得咁係積非成是,但係我覺得冇所謂亂用一事<br />\n就好似中英夾雜,突然出現既話你當然會覺得係亂黎,但係因為咁既方式已經有相對長既歷史同原因,已經變左一樣新野,成為左香港語言文化既一部分,所以我覺得稱唔上錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16109d17b365237e8d4f4ad75b967caa6e8019a1","tid":442030,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T01:14:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一個英國都有幾百種口音，成撚日互相笑大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當中以紐卡素口音最撚難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果scot都計既話我覺得Scottish accent最難頂,完全聽唔明,溝通都有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇咁多年波都聽唔明費格遜up乜柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9f35feb437af73ae9fd3ea292c6874a70392c6","tid":442030,"uid":109726,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T01:30:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CrRgm7KtUw4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCrRgm7KtUw4&d=A7kOZpoo0mE6aRkvZ0BVTdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8036a111\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CrRgm7KtUw4</a>"},{"pid":"21c18fd9dbe25b807531979be7555276208e5140","tid":442030,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T01:32:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一個英國都有幾百種口音，成撚日互相笑大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當中以紐卡素口音最撚難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果scot都計既話我覺得Scottish accent最難頂,完全聽唔明,溝通都有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前睇葉麗儀去蘇格蘭做節目<br />\n連佢都話聽唔明佢地講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5909a6198a215c36fe39a3ccffb2183b365f517","tid":442030,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T01:33:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[url<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CrRgm7KtUw4[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCrRgm7KtUw4%5B%2Furl%5D&d=A7kOZpoo0mE6aRkvZ0BVTdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=66d9081f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CrRgm7KtUw4[/url]</a></blockquote><br />\n好耐之前有個講口音既post見過,冇錯就係呢種,感覺同聲同氣咁好撚過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma