a-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CrRgm7KtUw4[/url]</a></blockquote><br />\n好耐之前有個講口音既post見過,冇錯就係呢種,感覺同聲同氣咁好撚過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港口音辨識度真係超高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好有親切感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲鬼佬勁鍾意lok</blockquote><br />\n間中有啲友屌聽唔明佢口音，但都好多鬼佬反屌返佢轉頭"},{"pid":"63aab7fdd09cd033f70bc8af2147f0cee1cbc1b8","tid":442030,"uid":77533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T02:38:12.000Z","msg":"中學老師話齋<br />\n講得夠順暢先追求口音呢啲嘢啦<br />\n當然，口音同你讀到個字錯晒又係兩回事嚟"},{"pid":"6c53d9a596265796c03ac38ff60e0c0ea63d2f03","tid":442030,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T02:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實口音有咩問題<br />\n以前咩國藉都有，基本上明你講咩就得<br />\n英文做first language唔代表易明佢講咩，你睇印度佬就明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽到好爭扎<br />\n尤其係講得快果時<br />\nLalala Matata"},{"pid":"9df65210c2a06a91777e8906f4827a4439ae607a","tid":442030,"uid":30535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T02:52:21.000Z","msg":"實際上港式英文係唔好聽，不過我又唔會話唔鍾意"}]}